channel.title: If you play Runescape private server, read
channel.description:
I am trying to collect information to help my (and anyone elses) server. ;)
What are the 5 things you look for in a private server
For example
[code]1. No lag 2. Lots of npcs to kill 3. Fast exp 4. Fun minigames 5. Skills[/code]
